{"tid":2084824,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"TED練listening睇唔睇字幕先？","createTime":"2020-06-29T13:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T06:34:20.000Z","uid":10424,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd743df52487b2bf58159cca5b62bd8e31eb1f9f","tid":2084824,"uid":10424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"有冇英文達人講下睇TED練listening,應該聽一次冇字幕然再聽有字幕，定相反會有郊練好英文listening?"},{"pid":"029aa3213ee2df1e243e616042e367f04953788d","tid":2084824,"uid":290640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"試下冇字幕聽一次先 睇下明幾多？"},{"pid":"396e6c25c492411e96e929fc8f2e2210c576f951","tid":2084824,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:27:33.000Z","msg":"睇咩topic<br />\n同埋條友咩口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得練英文最好睇同一個英文youtuber / 同一套sitcom<br />\n慣佢地口音先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8b0009ac8f23d26dbe1f32742e265d196f4b82","tid":2084824,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd743df52487b2bf58159cca5b62bd8e31eb1f9f","tid":2084824,"uid":10424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"有冇英文達人講下睇TED練listening,應該聽一次冇字幕然再聽有字幕，定相反會有郊練好英文listening?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:58:12.000Z","msg":"咁多 tv show 唔睇, 睇 TED...<br />\n<br />\n如果你想練嘅, 我建議你唔好開字幕. 會訓練到個腦依賴字幕, 跟住就成世都開字幕...<br />\n<br />\n另外無記錯, BBC News 啲字幕係有延遲 (3-4秒). 你可以試下用嚟訓練.<br />\n<br />\n或者不如唔好睇, 聽下 BBC Radio 1好過.<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 有好多嘢睇, 唔好咁悶睇 TED talk (雖然呢啲真係純粹個人喜好)<br />\n<br />\n(利申平時 1.5x/2x 開字幕)"},{"pid":"d0ca753d0a79b7fee7f05abad2dc2893fd809e90","tid":2084824,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T20:42:37.000Z","msg":"要睇字幕<br />\n<br />\n利申DSE5**<br />\n<br />\nIELTS 8.0"},{"pid":"f582654ff4ceccdb3078e58fc824b82414705e6a","tid":2084824,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T20:46:46.000Z","msg":"睇你想練乜<br />\n練純listening 就冇字幕<br />\n練語感 + listening就睇埋字幕<br />\n練即時理解力就用張白紙抄低個speaker講過你又覺得有重嘅point<br />\n睇下可唔可以明白哂佢講咩<br />\n同時個腦又可以記住佢講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申都係用1.5/2.0倍速聽開YouTube"},{"pid":"76985d4870252013716084ae9e49ff715e8f0e90","tid":2084824,"uid":47384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0ca753d0a79b7fee7f05abad2dc2893fd809e90","tid":2084824,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T20:42:37.000Z","msg":"要睇字幕<br />\n<br />\n利申DSE5**<br />\n<br />\nIELTS 8.0"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}